# Leetspeak Converter

A Python tool to convert text to leetspeak and back.

## Features

- Convert normal text to leetspeak
- Convert leetspeak back to normal text
- Preserves case sensitivity
- Command-line interface
- Includes unit tests

## Usage

To convert text to leetspeak:
```bash
python main.py to-leet "your text here"
```

To convert leetspeak back to text:
```bash
python main.py to-text "y0ur 73x7 h3r3"
```

For help and system message:
```bash
python main.py --help
```

## Examples

```bash
$ python main.py to-leet "hello world"
Original: hello world
Leetspeak: h3110 w0r1d

$ python main.py to-text "h3110 w0r1d"
Leetspeak: h3110 w0r1d
Original: hello world
```

## Testing

Run the unit tests with:
```bash
python -m unittest test_leetspeak.py
```